item.prore.blasting_argument.desc: Limits the machine to only blasting recipes but improves the speed
item.prore.blasting_argument.tooltip.1: Increases the speed of the machine by 100%
item.prore.blasting_argument.tooltip.2: Limits the machine to only blasting recipes
item.prore.efficiency_upgrade.desc: Decreases the power consumption of the machine
item.prore.efficiency_upgrade.tooltip.1: Decreases the power consumption of the machine by 50%
item.prore.efficiency_upgrade.tooltip.2: Decreases the speed of the machine by 25%
item.prore.overclock_argument.desc: Increases the speed of the machine but increases the power consumption
item.prore.overclock_argument.tooltip.1: Increases the speed of the machine by a factor of 2
item.prore.overclock_argument.tooltip.2: Increases the power consumption of the machine by a factor of 4
item.prore.smoking_argument.desc: Limits the machine to only smoking recipes but improves the speed
item.prore.smoking_argument.tooltip.1: Increases the speed of the machine by 100%
item.prore.smoking_argument.tooltip.2: Limits the machine to only smoking recipes
item.prore.speed_upgrade.desc: Increases the speed of the machine
item.prore.speed_upgrade.tooltip.1: Increases the speed of the machine by 100%
item.prore.speed_upgrade.tooltip.2: Increases the power consumption of the machine by 200%
prore.info.arguments: §7In these slots you can add arguments to make your machine do different things!
prore.info.upgrades: §7In these slots you can add upgrades to make your machine better!
